 _Swngcharni thani Elven-habugrarokni bagwi Ring tham,
 Dwarf-lordrokni bagwi bórokni holongni hallrogo snichi,
 Thwina bagwi chongjak Mortal borokrokni bagwi 9,
 Khoroksa bini mwnakma achukthayungo tongnai mwnakma Subraiyungni bagwi
 Mordor ni hasteo Shadows tongmani.
 Bohrokno bebakno tẃinani bagwi kaisa Ring, Bórokno manna bagwi kaisa Ring,
 Bohrokno bebak tubuna bagwi tei mwnakmao bohrokno khaina bagwi kaisa Ring
 Mordor ni hasteo Shadows tongmani._
