 _ni puila part wngwi
 Ringrokni Subrai_
 BUKU I
 _Kwthar 1_
 Kwbangma jorani bagwi khatungjak party
 Bag End ni Mr. Bilbo Baggins bo kwchak kuphur khe wngnai hwnwi sakha.
bini chisa-chisa achaima salno khatungma bai palaiwi,
Hobbiton o kwbángma kok salaijak tei khá torjak.
 Bilbo belai kheno rangchak tei belai kheno uanamasingcha, tei bini uanamasingcha wngwi tongmani
Shire bisi chisni jora, bini uanamasingcha khe kwmamani tei uansukjakya
kiphilmani. Bo bini himmani bisingtwi tubumani rangchakrok tabuk local wngwi thangkha .
legend, tei abo lukurok poito khlaio, kwcham borok tamo sa phano, abo
Bag End ni Hill o rangchak bai supungjak tunnelrok bai kupulung wng kha. Tei abo wngma hwnkhe
mung kotorni bagwi nang ya, aro bini kwbángma jora tongmani phanbo tongo, uanamasingcha wngna bagwi. Jora
wngkha, phiya ba Mr. Baggins ni sakao abo belai kheno wngma hai wngkha. Bo wngkha
50 bisini hai kheno. Hakhe bohrok bono _kaham_- hwnwi ringnani chengkha.
mwthangjak, phiya _swlaijakya_ mark ni ganao tongnai. Kwbangma tongmani
abo bórokni bokhorokno swngwi rw kha tei omo belai kaham samung hwnwi uansuk kha; Obo
jesa phano borok (nugwi) mol brúm brúm sikla wngwi tongna nangmani abo kaham ya hwnwi nukjago
as (reputed) wngwi thangnai rang-ri.
 ‘Aboni bagwi rang rwna nangnai,’ hwnwi bórok sa kha. 'Omo swkangni kok ya, tei jwngjal
aboni bising tẃi phainai!’
 Tamo khe tabuk jora jora jwngjal phai ya kho; tei Mr. Baggins bini
rang, borok kwbángma bono bini aswk hamya tei bini kahamrokno nakarwi mano
kwpal kaham. Bo bini núkhungni borok bai malainani bagwi tongwi kha (chaya, kubui khe,
Sackville-Baginses), tei bini hobbitrokni bisingo kwbángma khá tornai bororok tongo
kwrwi tei nangkukya nukhungrokni. Tamo khe bini kaisa hamjaknai kwrwi, baksa
bini bwsarok torwi phainani chengkha.
 Bohrokni bisingo kotorkuk, tei Bilbo ni hamjakma wngkha chwrai Frodo Baggins. Buphuru
Bilbo wngkha 99 bisi, bo Frodo no bini heir wngwi rwkha, tei bono kwthang tongna bagwi tubukha
Bag ni paithago; tei Sakvi-Baginsrokni khatungmarok paithago thwiwi thang kha.
Bilbo tei Frodo ni achaima sal wngkha, September talni 22 salmari. 'Nwng mankha
kaham khe phaiwi o jagao tong di, Frodo ani bwsa,’ hwnwi Bilbo salsa sa kha; 'tei aboni ulo chwng mano
chini achaima sal-partyrokno kwchang kwchang khe khlai di.’ A jorao Frodo
tabukbo bini _tweens_o tongo, hobbitrok samung kwrwi bisiknwi hwnwi sajakma hai
chwrai wngmani tei thamchi-thamni umor wngmani bisingo.
 Tei bisi chisni wngwi thangkha. Bisi bisi kheno Baggins rok belai kheno kwthang khe rw lai kha
Bag End o achaima sal-pandarok; Tamo khe tabuk bujijak kha, mungsa swk
a autumn ni bagwi belai kheno swkangni plan khlaijak tongmani. Bilbo wngna bagwi thangkha
_chisa-chisa,_ 111, kaisa belai kheno khá torjak nambar tei belai kheno borom rwjak umor
hobbit (Old Took sak sak 130 bisini simi se sók phai kha); tei Frodo wngna bagwi
_thamchi-thamchi,_ 33) kaisa nangkukmani number: bini ‘umor phaimani sal’.
 Hobbiton tei Biwater-o kók tháisa wngwi tháng kha; tei phainani kok
event Shire gwnangwi tháng kha. Mr. Bilbo ni koktwma tei tongmung
Baggins tei kaisa kok salainani kotor kok wngkha; tei okra borok
suddenly bohrokni muiturokno hamjakmani demand-o mankha.
 Kwcham Ham Gamgee ni slai khoroksa phano belai kheno naisingwi tongnai kwrwi, jotono sinijak
Gaffer hai khe. Bo _Ivy Bush_-o tongwi kha, twijlangni saka-o tongnai nok kwchwng.
lahar; tei bo kaisa phan bai kók sa kha, tamni hwn ba bo Bag .
End nokha bisi brwichi jora, tei aboni swkang Holman nobo abo hai samungno chubachu khlai kha.
Tabuk bo sak sakno bwrwi wngwi thangkha tei joint-o stiff wngwi thangkha, aboni bagwi samung wngkha
bini bwsla kotor Sam Gamgee bai wngwi tongmani. Bupha bai bwsa khoroknwi’-no
Bilbo tei Frodo bai belai kheno kwrwngwi tongmani. Bórok Hill-o sak baithang tong lai kha, 1990 bisi-o.
Bag End ni thani 3 nombor Bagshot Row.
 'Kaisa belai kaham kok sanai borok wngkha Mr. Bilbo, ang swkang swkang khe samani hai
hwnwi sa kha,’ hwnwi Gaffer sa kha. Kubui kok bai: tamni hwnba Bilbo belai kheno lachimasingcha
bono, bono ‘Master Hamfast’ hwnwi ringwi, tei bini thani wngwi tongnai
wngwi tongmani – ‘root’ ni koktwi, khatijak khe alu,
Gaffer no kamiyung ni joto borok bai kotor wngnai hwnwi sinijak kha
(bo sak bai baksa).
 'Phiyaba bini logi tongnai Frodo ni kok tamo?' swngkha kwcham Noakes
Twi bai. ‘Baggins wngkha bini mung, phiya bo Brandy ni slái kwbángma, hwnwi bórok sa-o.
Hobbiton ni jesa phano Baggins tamoni bagwi bihik naitukna bagwi thangnai
aro Buckland-o, aro bororok belai kheno lachimasingcha.’
 'Tei uanamasingcha ya, bohrok queer wngkha,' hwnwi Daddy Twofoot (Gaffer ni ganani ganani borok) sakha, 'bohrok 1990 bisio tongwi tongkhe.
Brandywine twima ni bwkhak, tei
rwngthoma agin. Obo kaisa mwnakma hamya jaga, koktwmarokni baksa wngkhe
kubui.'
 'Nwng wngkha, baba!' hwnwi Gafer sakha. ‘Bucklandni Brandybukrok _Kwtal_ Hayungni bisingo tongmani abo ya; Phiya
bohrok kaisa queer jati, nukjakgo. Bohrok hamya
a twijlang kotorni saka-o rungrok bai khe – tei abo natural ya. Kwchak uanamasingcha
jwngjal wng kha, ang sa-o. Tamo khe jesa phano wngthung, Mr. Frodo chwrai hai kheno kaham
