Drogo Bagins; bo twio thwiwi thang ya sak bini kókno kwbángma sajak li ya.’
 'Twio klaikha?' hwnwi kwbangma khorang sakha. Bórok omo hai khe khna kha tei tei mwnakma
rumors swkang, wng kha; Tamo khe hobbitrokni nukhungni koktwmani bagwi belai kheno hamjakma tongo, tei
bórok tei uáisa khnana bagwi tiyar wng lai kha. ‘Kaham, abo hai kheno bórok sa-o,’ hwnwi Gaffer sa kha. 'Nwng
naidi: Mr. Drogo, bo kwrwi miss primula bai kasajak kha. Bo chini Mr.
Bilbo ni puila cousin buma ni bwkhak (bini buma wngkha
Old Took ni bwsajwkrok); tei Mr. Drogo khe bini bwsajwk. Hakhe Mr. Frodo
bini puila _tei_ cousin, kaisa jorao jesa phano lamao swkakjak, kok sanani hai,
nwng ano rwktharwi tongkhe. Tei Mr. Drogo bini buphani bwsajwk bai baksa brandy hall o tongwi tongmani,
bo bini kaijakmani ulo kwbangma jora khlaima hai (bo wngwi
bini rangchakni thani thángnai, tei Gorbadoc bwrwima kaisa phan gwnang rangchakni tableno narwknai); tei
bo _boat_o Brandwine twima saka-o tháng kha; tei bini bihik bai
thwi kha, tei kwrwi Mr. Frodo khoroksa chwrai tei jotono. '
 'Ang khna kha bohrok salni pohor bai chámung cháui twi saka-o tháng lai kha,' hwnwi sa kha
Noak kwcham; 'tei abo Drogo ni rangchak hai khe rungno twio klai kha.'
 'Tei _ang_ khna kha bo bono thwiwi rwkha, tei boh bono bini ulo thwiwi rwkha,' hwnwi sakha
Sandyman, Hobiton ni borok.
 ‘Nwng khnamani bebak kokrokno khnana nangya, Sandyman,’ hwnwi Gaffer sakha, bo
miller no belai khe hamjak ya. 'Pushing ni kok sanani bagwi call kwrwi
tei tẃiwi. Boat rok belai kheno tricky wngkha abo kwrwi khe achuknai rokni bagwi
jwngjalni karonno teibo naituk lai kha. Jesa phano wngthung: aro o Mr. Frodo tongo
nwng samani hai, a bucklanders rokni bisingo khoroksa bwsa kwrwi tei thwiwi thangkha,
