 A talni bisingo September tal wngkha, tei nwng swngwi mano hai kheno kaham. Salsa eba salnwi
ulo kaisa rumor (kwrwngnai Sam bai chengjak) 1990 ni koktwi chapjak kha.
abo wngkha hórjlai wngnai – hórjlai, tamo wngnai, jesa khe
Shire o 100 bisini simi nukjakya, kubui’-no swkangni simi nukjakya
Took thwikha.
 Sal wngwi thangkha tei The Day gana wngwi phaikha. Kaisa aswk nukjaknai waggon
salsa horo Hobbiton o phaikha tei hathái sakao samung tangwi thángkha
Bag ni paithago. Hobbitrok uanajak hobbitrok lamplitni dugarrokni phataro naiwi abono naina bagwi naiwi tongkha. Obo
Phatarni borok bai tlangjak kha, aswk uanamasingcha rwchapmung rwchap kha: dwarves kuchuk dakha
tei kwrak hood. Bohrokni bisingo khoroknwi khoroktham Bag End o tongwi kha. Second ni paithago
September talni bisingo kaisa malkhung Bywater bising tẃi phai kha
Brandy wine bridge wngkha salni pohor. Khoroksa okra borok sak bai sak drive khlaiwi tongmani. Boro
kaisa kotor kotor rangchakni hat, kaisa kotor rangchakni rí, tei rangchakni scarf kanwi tongo. Boh ni kaisa
bini hat ni bwskangni phatarni rangchak kwchak tei bushy mokol.
Hobbit-chwrairok Hobbiton bising tẃi cart ni ulo khárwi tháng lai kha tei tháng lai kha
hapung hathai. Aboni bisingo rangchakni cargo tongo, bórok kaham khe uansukma hai. Bilbo ni bwskango
dugar okra borok phiyokna chengkha: aro bebakni hórjlai kotorma bundles tongo
rangchak tei rangchak, khoroksa khoroksano kaisa kotor rangchak G bai swijak tei elf-rune, .
 Obo Gandalf ni mari, kubui, tei borok kotor wngkha Gandalf
Wizard, bini mung gwnang Shire o bini skill ni bagwi wngkha,
nwng, tei nwng. Bini kubui samung belai kheno hamya tei kirimasingcha wngkha,
tamo khe Shire-ni bororok aboni kókno mungsabo saui man li ya. Bórokni bagwi bo wng kha khoroksa
Party ni 'atrak' wngkha. Aboni bagwino hobbit-chwrairokni khá tormani. 'G
Grandni bagwi!' bórok chirikhók lai kha, hakhe a borok kotorma khá kham kha. Bórok bono nukma bai’-no sini kha.
tamo khe bo Hobbiton-o jora jora khe simi nukjak kha tei kwbángma jora tongwi man li ya; Phiya
bórok eba khoroksa phano bórokni okrarokni bere kotorkuk simi se bini khoroksano nuk ya kho
rangchakni phuarjakmarok – bohrok tabuk legendary swkangni jorani wngwi thangkha.
 A borok kotor, Bilbo tei khoroknwi khoroktham dwarfrok bai chubajak khe, samung tangwi pái kha
rwchapmung. Bilbo rang kwcharo rwkha; tamo khe khoroksa phano squib eba cracker ya
wng kha, nainairokni kha khamjakma bai.
 'Tabuk khárwi tháng di!' hwnwi sakha. ‘Jora phai khe nwng kwbángma mannai.’
Hakhe bo Bilbo bai baksa nok bisingo kwmawi thangkha, tei dugar phiyogwi rwkha. Chwrairok
Hobbits rok belai kheno dugar no naisigwi tongkha, tei aboni ulo thwngwi thangkha, uansukwi
party ni sal phai glak hwnwi.
 Bag End ni bisingo, Bilbo tei Gandalf khoroksa
room kotor khe west bwkhak khe kheto bwkhak naiwi tongo. Salni sal belai kheno wngkha
tei kwchangma. Buphangrok kwchak tei rangchak hai khe torwi phai kha: snap-dragons tei salni-bwrwirok,
tei nasturtiumrok bebak turfni bwkhak tẃiwi thángwi tongo tei kwcharo naisigwi tongo
khotolrok.
 'Nini kheto bahai khe rangchak nukjak!' hwnwi sakha.
 ‘Hai’ hwnwi Bilbo sakha. Ang belai kheno hamjago, tei jotono hamjaknai bwrwirokno
Shire; tamo khe ang uansugo ang holiday nangnai.’
 'Nwng nini plan bai swkang thangna bagwi de?'
 'Ang khlaio. Ang ani kháno tal kwbángma swkang’-no swnam kha, tei ang abono swlaiwi man li ya.’
 ‘Belai kaham. Abo tei kaisa kók kaham ya. Nini plan o tongdi – nini
Puilani plan, bwkha – tei ang kha khlaio abo kahamni bagwi, nini thani, tei
chwng jotono.’
 'Ang abono wansugo. Jesa phano wngthung ang sakno tongthokna muchungo, tei ani chwrai
kara.'
 'Sabo lachinai, ang uanajak?' Gandalf bokhorok swngwi sakha.
 ‘Chwng nuknai,’ hwnwi Bilbo sakha.
