phiya Bilbo swkangni simi’-no kwtal kwtal rwchapmungrok rwwi tongmani, tei manmani manwirokno rwwi tongmani. O
hole kwthar tabuk kisa clear wngwi tongkha.
 Jukjak juda juda khakchangmani rwchapmungrokni bebakno label tongo, sak bai sak swijak
Bilbo bai, tei kwbangma point, eba joke tongo. Tamo khe, kubui khe, kwbángma
manwirokno bórok muchungma tei yachakjaknai jagao rwjak kha. Kwplaisa
hobbitrok, tei aswk khe Bagshot Rowni borokrok belai kaham khe khlai kha. Kwcham Gaffer Gamgee
nwi sack alu, kaisa spade kwtal, kaisa rangchakni waistcoat, tei kaisa botol mankha
joint wngna bagwi ointment. Kwcham Rory brandybak, kwbangma rangni bagwi
hamjakma bai, kwcham winyards ni dozen botol mankha: kaisa kwrak angur bwtwi
Saka-o thángnai, tei tabuk belai kheno torjak, Bilbo bai swnamjakma hai khe
pha. Rory Bilbo no belai kheno nakarkha, tei
puila botol.
 Frodo ni bagwi jotono kwbangma tongkha. Tei, kubui khe, bebak
kotor kotor rangchak, abo hai kheno bijap, mangpili, tei nangmani slái kwbángma
furniture, bini yakni rwjak kha. Tamo khe, mungsa phano sign kwrwi
rang eba rangchak ni kok sanani: rang-ri eba glass ni rangchak rwjakya
hakchalo.
 Frodo a salo belai kheno try khlaikha. Kaisa tatal kokthai
bebak nokni bororokno hór hai khe free spread khlaiwi rwjak kha; tei swkang
Kwbangma jora a jaga borok bai kupulung wngkha, bohrokni aro samung kwrwi, phiya manliya
phatarni tonjak. Labels rok thwiwi thangkha tei mix wngwi thangkha, tei wngwi thangkha. Baksa
borokrok hall-o swap tei deal khlaina bagwi try khlai kha; tei kubuirok _off_ khwlainani chaitokkha
Chikon manwirok bai bohrokno address khlaijakya, eba jesa phano manwirok bai muchungjakya hwnwi nukjak
eba naijakya. Gate thángna bagwi lama barja tei yakni malkhungrok bai chapjak.
 Hakhe wngwi tongmani bisingo Sakvili-Baginsesrok phai kha. Frodo
kisa jorani bagwi retire wngkha tei bini bachanai merry brandybuck no naisingwi tongna bagwi yakarwi thangkha
manwi-khwnwirok. Otho Frodo no nukna bagwi khorang kotor khe san phuru, Merry lachima bai khulumkha.
 ‘Bo hamya wng kha,’ hwnwi bo sa kha. 'Bo rest wngwi tongkha.'
 ‘Hidi, nwng sakha,’ hwnwi Lobelia sakha. 'Jesa phano wngthung chwng bono nukna muchungo tei chwng mean
bono nukna bagwi. Just thángwi bono hai hwnwi sa di!’
 Merry bohrokno hall o kwbangma jora rwkha, tei bohrok saimanna bagwi jora mankha
bórokni khármani rwngthoma. Abo bórokni khá hamyano kaham khlai li ya. Paithago
bórokno study-o phunukjak kha. Frodo kaisa table sakao kwbangma manwirok bai baksa achukwi tongmani
bini bwskango paperrok tongo. Bo khá hamya wngwi nukjak kha – Sackville-Bagginses no nukna bagwi
jesa phano rate; tei bini pocket-o mungsa swk manwi tẃiwi bachaui tháng kha. Tamo khe bo
belai kheno polite khe kok sakha.
 Sakni borokrok belai kheno khá khamjak. Bohrok bono yapharnani chengkha
hamya bargain-mung (dopharokni bisingo hai) kwbangma manwi tei mung kwrwini bagwi
manwi-khwnwirok. Frodo hai hwnwi sakha, Bilbo khakchangma bai swnamjak manwirok simi se
rwjakmani, bórok sa kha, bebak affair belai kheno fishy.
 ‘Kaisa kok simi se ani thani klaijak,’ hwnwi Otho sakha, ‘tei abo wngkha nwng .
aboni bising tẃi belai kaham khe khlaiwi. Ang will no nukna bagwi insist khlaio.’
 Otho Bilbo ni heir wngnai, phiya Frodo no adopt khlainani bagwi. Bo porikha
will no khá khárwi tei snort khlai kha. Abo, khatungma bai, belai kheno klaijak tei thik
(Hobbits ni raida ni tongmung bai, abo tei kubun manwirokni bisingo sanwi tongo
sakhirokni 7 signature red ink bai swijak).
