 ‘Angbo hai’-no hai,’ hwnwi Gandalf sa kha. ‘Tei ang teibo kwbángma samungrokno khá khamjago. Tabuk kaham khe tongdi!
Sakno naikoldi! Ani thani nai di, khatijak jora-o! Thangkha!'
 Frodo bono dugar bwskango nuk kha. Bo bini yakno paithago yapharkha, tei himkha
off wng kha uanamasingcha pace; tamo khe Frodo uansuk kha a kwcham wizard aswk khe nukjak
