bono teibo kwbángma jorani bagwi.
 _Kwthar 2_
 swkangni salni mwkhang
 Talk 9 eba 99 salni bisingo thwiwi thangliya. Tei kaisa
Bilbo Baggins ni kwmajakma kokno hobbiton o kok salaikha, tei kubui khe jotono
Shire ni sakao, bisi kaisa tei salsa jora, tei 1990 bisini slái kwbángma jora muitu khlaijak kha.
Abo. Abo hobbit siklarokni bagwi kaisa hór-kothoma wngwi tháng kha; tei paithago Mad
Baggins, bo kaisa bangwi tei phan bai khe kwmawi thango tei
rangchak tei rangchak, legend ni hamjakma borok wngkha tei kwbangma jora tongwi kha
bebak kubui wngmarokno pogwi thangmani ulo.
 Tamo khe aboni bisingo, kamiyungni jotoni uansukmung wngkha
Bilbo, bo jora jora khe belai kheno khá khamjak, bo belai kheno khá kham kha, tei
Blue ni bisingo tháng di. Aro bo uansukma kwrwi khe twijlang eba twijlangni bisingo klai kha
tei belai kheno khá khárjak, phiya ba jora kwrwi khe páiwi thangnai. Blame no belai kheno rwjak kha
Gandalf ni sakao.
 'A dratted wizard simi se Frodo sikla no yakarwi thangkhe, wngwi mano bo
settle wng di tei hobbit-swngmung wng di,’ hwnwi bórok sa kha. Tei bebak nukjakmani
Wizard Frodo no sak sak yakarwi thangkha, tei boh tongwi kha, phiya ba tormani
hobbit-sense belai kheno nukjakya. Puila, bo kaisa jora-o’-no swkang thángna cheng kha
Bilbo ni mung kotor wngkha. Bo khá khamma-o thángna muchung ya; tei ulo
bisio bo Bilbo ni sa-chi-nwi achaima salno khulumna bagwi kaisa party khlai kha, abo
bo Sajla-Kwtal Panda hwnwi mung rw kha. Tamo khe abo markni slái kwrwi wng kha, tamni hwn ba 20
bisingo phainairokno ringjak kha tei aro kwbangma chámung tongo aro chámung snow wng kha tei
uaisa nungmani, hobbitrok samani hai.
 Baksa bororok belai kheno khá khamjak kha; tamo khe Frodo rwmani charimungno tẃiwi tong kha
Bilbo ni achaima salni party bisi bisi khe bohrok thwngwi thangma jora. Bo hai hwnwi sakha
bo Bilbo thwikha hwnwi uansukliya. Bórok swng khe: ‘Hakhe bo bahai khe tong?’ Boro
bini yago shrug khlai kha.
 Bo sak sak tongwi kha, Bilbo khlaima hai; Tamo khe bo kwbángma bachanairok tongo,
khairokma khe sikla hobbitrokni bisingo (kwbangma khe Old Took ni bwsarok) bohrok
chwrai wngwi Bilbo no hamjakgo tei kwbangma jora Bag End o hapwi phaio. Folco
Boffin tei Fredegar Bolger wngkha khoroknwi; tamo khe bini hamjakma borok
Peregrin Took (kwbangma jorao Pippin hwnwi sajak), tei Merry Brandybuck (bini mung kubui
Meriadoc, tamo khe abo belai kheno muitu khlaijak). Frodo bebak jagao himwi tháng kha
Bórok bai baksa wng di; tamo khe kwbángma jora bo sak bai sak thángwi tong kha, hakhe bórok uanajak kha
Buj thumnai borokrokni bisingo bo kebo kebo khe nokni hakchal hathái-o himwi tongma nukjago tei
swngcharni pohorni thani tongnai buphangrok. Merry tei Pippin uansukkha bo
Elves rok jora jora, Bilbo khlaima hai.
 Jora wngwi phaima bai, borokrok nuknani chengkha Frodobo 1990 bisini mari phunukkha.
kaham 'chammung': phatarni nukmung bo robust tei
bini tweens ni bisingo tongnai. 'Kwbangma borok ni joto luck tongo,' bohrok
samani; Tamo khe abo Frodo 1990 bisini belai kheno sober umor sók phai ya sak wng kha.
fifty hwnwi bórok uansukna cheng kha.
 Frodo sak sak, puila shock wngmani ulo, bini sakni nokphang wngwi tei
_Bag End ni Mr. Baggins belai kheno khá khárjak. Kwbangma bisini bagwi bo belai kheno
happy tei bwskangni bagwi belai uanajakya. Tamo khe bo sakno saimanya
Bilbo bai baksa thangya hwnwi khá khá khá wngwi tongmani. Bo sakno mankha
jora jora khe uanajak, khakchangma jorao, hasing panthorrokni kok, tei
bo nuk ya kho hatháini uanamasingcha nukmungrok bini kukma-o phai kha. Boro
bo sakno hai hwnwi sa kha: ‘Phiyaba ang sak baithang salsa twijlangno swkaknai.’ No
je bini bwkhani tei kaisa bwkhak jora jora khe hai hwnwi answer rw-o: ‘Tabuk jora ya.’
 Hakhe abo hai kheno wngwi tong kha, bini bisi brwichi wngwi thang kha, tei bini bisi 50 wngwi thang kha.
achaima sal gana phaikha: bachi wngkha kaisa number je bo bahai khe phano uansukkha
kotor (eba hamya); abo jesa phano wngthung a umor o adventure tongmani
wngkha Bilbo. Frodo khá khamjakna cheng kha, tei lama kwthar
belai kaham khe trod wngjak hwnwi nukjak kha. Bo maprokno naikha, tei bohrokni bwskango tamo tong hwnwi uanajak
edges: Shire-o swnamjak map-o bini borderni phatarni kwbángma rangchakni jagarokno phunukjak kha.
Bo teibo hakchal khe tei kwbángma jora sak bai sak thángna bagwi tháng kha; tei tongthokma tei
bini kubun bachanairok bono khá khárwi naisigwi tong lai kha. Kwbangma jorao bo himwi tei kok salai tongma nukjago
o jora-o Shire-o nukjakna bagwi chengjak uanamasingcha lama-o himnairok bai.
 Phiyaba phatarni swngcharo aswk uanamasingcha samungrok wngwi tongo hwnwi kok chapjak kha; tei
tamni hwnba Gandalf a jorao nukjakya eba mungsa swk koktwma rohorya
bisi, Frodo bo wngwi manmani bebak khorangrokno thumkha. Elves, bohrok kwbangma jorao himya
Shire, tabuk salka jora-o buphang bising tẃi salka bwkhak thángma nukjak kha,
passing tei kiphilwi phai ya; Tamo khe bórok swngcharni kwcharo tháng lai kha tei wng li ya
bini jwngjalrokni bagwi kwbángma jora khá khamjak. Tamo khe, lamao dwarfrok tongmani
aswk number o. Kwcham salthang-salthang lama Shire bising tẃi bini
Gray Havens-o pái kha, tei dwarfrok bórokni
Blue hathái-o tongnai. Bohrok hobbitrokni khorongni kotor source wngkha
hasing panthor – bohrok mungsa swk muchungkhe: kerong hai khe dwarfs rok kisa kok sakha tei hobbits
tei swng li ya. Tamo khe tabuk Frodo kwbangma jorao hakchal haste ni uanamasingcha dwarf rok bai malai kha.
Westni bwkhak khárwi thángna bagwi naituk lai kha. Bórok belai khe uanajak kha, hakhe baksa khe .
Satrai tei Mordor Hayungni.
 O mungno hobbitrok swkangni mwnakma koktwmarogo simi se saimankha, hai
bórokni muituni bwskango shadow; tamo khe abo hamya wngkha tei
uanamasingcha. Mirkwood ni phan hamya no 1990 bisi bai rwktharwi rohorjakma hai khe nukjak kha.
White council kwmajak kwrak jagao teibo phan bai nukjakna bagwi simi se
Mordor ni. Dark Tower no swnamjak kha hwnwi sajak kha. Aroni simi phan
belai kheno hasing panthor khe thángwi tong kha, hasing panthor bai salka bwkhak choba wng kha tei
kirima torwi phaikha. Orcs rok hathái sakao teibo kwbángma wngwi tong kha. Troll wngkha
phatar ha-o, tabuk dull-witt wng ya, tamo khe khá khamjak tei kirimasingcha manwi-khwnwirok bai swprakjak.
Hakhe aboni slái khe kirimasingcha snamjakrokni kókrok wng kha, tamo khe .
bórokni mung kwrwi.
 O jotoni bisingo kisa kheno, kubui khe, samung tangnai hobbitrokni khukni thani sók phai kha. Phiya
wngwi tongmani tei nogo tongnairokbo queer kokrok khnanani chengkha; tei abo
bórokni business bórokno border-o tubu-ui uanamasingcha samungrok nuk kha. Kok salaimani
Bywater o _Kwchak Dragon_ o, Frodo ni salsa horo
50th bisi, phunukkha abo Shire ni kokthairokni khakchangma bwkhao phano
khnajak kha, phiya kwbángma hobbitrok tabukbo bórokno lachijak.
 Sam Gamgee khoroksa thani hór gana-o achukwi tongmani, tei bini bwskango .
Ted Sandyman, bini bwsla; tei aro kwbangma rustic hobbits tongo
bórokni kók khnaui.
 ‘Queer kokrok nwng o salrogo khnao, sure wngna bagwi,’ hwnwi Sam sakha.
 ‘Ah,’ Ted sakha, ‘nwng khlai di, nwng khna khe. Tamo khe ang hórjlai-kothoma khnawi mano tei
chwrairokni koktwma nogo, ang muchung khe.’
 ‘No doubt nwng khlaiwi mano,’ Sam hai hwnwi sa kha, ‘tei ang daresay 1990 bisio teibo kubui kok tongo.
bórokni bere baksa norok uansukmani slái. Jesa phano wngthung koktwmarokno sabo invent khlaikha? Dragonrokno nai di
