tei bankni bwkhakni reedrokni bisingo steam hai khe khoroknwi khoroktham curling wisps wngwi tongo. Aro
tei swkangni bwkhak fog kwrwi wngma hai khe nukjak kha.
 Merry pony no twijlangni lama sakao tubukha, tei teirok
rwngkha. Merry aboni ulo khe kaisa pole kotor bai slowly slow khe push khaikha. Brandy wine thwngkha
