winding lamao swkangni landingni simi tháng kha. Aro lamp wngwi tong kha.
Aboni ulo Buck Hasinglwng nukjak kha; tei aboni bisingni thángwi thángnai,
kwbángma round windowrok wng kha, rangchak tei rangchak. Bohrok Brandy ni khotol wngkha
Hall, Brandyrokni swkangni nogo.
 Kwplaisa jora swkang Gorhendad kwcham nukhungni bokhorok, kwcham nukhungni khoroksa
Marish-o eba Shire-o, twijlangno swkak kha, abo wng kha
hayungni swkangni boundary. Bo brandy hall swnamkha (tei duglam khaikha),
bini mungno Brandybuck hwnwi swlaiwi, tei tamo wngmani aboni nokphang wngna bagwi tongwi kha.
practically kaisa swkangni haste. Bini nukhung torwi phaikha tei torwi phaikha, tei bini ulo
sal kwbangma wngwi thangkha, Brandy Hall hathái bebakno romwi man ya sak,
aboni bwskangni dugar kotor tham, bwkhakni dugar kwbángma tei khorok chisa jora window tongo.
Brandybucks tei bohrokni kwbangma borokrok aboni ulo duglam thwngna chengkha, tei ulo
swnamna bagwi, bebak round. Abo Buckland ni wngwi phaimani, kaisa thick
twijlang bai kwcham hayungni bisingo tongnai strip, kaisa colony ni simi
shire ni. Bini kotor kamiyung wngkha Bucklebury, twijlang ganao kuthumjak tei
brandy hall ni bwskango.
 Marish ni borokrok Buckland ni borok bai kwrwngwi tong lai kha, tei
Hall ni bokhorokni phan (Brandybuck nukhungni bokhorok wngma hai
ringjak) Stock tei Rushey ni bisingo tongnai kheto tangnairok tabukbo swngwi tongo. Phiya
kwcham Shire ni borok kwbángma Bucklanders rokno aswk khe khá khamjak hwnwi uansugo, baksa
