 Kaisa dugar phiyokjak kha tei Tom Bombadil hap kha. Boh tabuk hat kwrwi tei bini thick
brown chuknohani rangchakni bwthairok bai crown khlaijak. Bo khá kham kha, tei Goldberryni thani tháng kha,
bini yak romkha.
 'Omo ani hamjakma bwrwi!' bo hobbitrokni thani khulumwi sakha. 'Omo ani
Goldberry bebak rangchak-kwchak rí bai kanwi bini yago rangchakrok kanwi! Tebol de
laden? Ang rangchakni krim bai rangchakni rangchak, tei rangchakni rangchak, tei rangchak nuk kha; dudh,
cheese, tei rangchakni bwthairok tei bwthairok thumjak kha. Abo chini thani nangmani da? Wngkha
