 _Kwtal 9_
 ni sign o
 Kwplaisa Korai_
 Bree wngkha Bree-hayungni kotor kami, khoroksa borok tongmani amchai,
bini gana-o tongnai khali ha-o kaisa island hai. Bree ni swlai, aro
Hathai ni tei bwkhak o tongdi, Combe kaisa kwrak hasing panthor o kisa swkang
salkabaini bwkhak tei Arket khe Chetwudni duglamo. Bree-hathái gwnangwi tongmani tei
kamiyungrok khe kheto-o tongnai ha kotor tei bwthai-bwthai kwrwi
kuwar.
 Bree ni borok rok brown-hair, kotor, tei belai kheno kwchak, tongthokjak tei
independent: bórok sakni bagwi simi se khoroksani wng ya; tamo khe bohrok kwbang wngkha
Hobbit, Dwarf, Elf, tei kubun tongnairok bai kwrwngjak tei saimanjak
swngchar bohrokni koktwi Big People bai swkangni slai (eba tongmani) slai. ni koktwi
bórokni sakni koktwmarok bórok wng kha swkangni tongnairok tei bórokni bwsarok wng kha
puila Borokrok wng kha, swngcharni kwcharni Westni bwkhak thángnai. Kwbangma
